ion and registration setting is efficient for reducing acquisition time\nand consequently motion artifacts for ultra-high resolution imaging of the\ninner structure of the hippocampus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 May 2016 12:38:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-10"}
